{"tid":24171,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"(求屌醒)諗住約人嗰一刻腦中閃過上一段感情","createTime":"2016-12-05T11:35:05.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-05T13:35:54.000Z","uid":1823,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"cacfac051daca287b4d8b46178552fd421746bd2","tid":24171,"uid":1823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T11:35:05.000Z","msg":"我係舊登問過點樣追補習miss，不過應該冇人記得我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁講少少資料先，我老闆係港島某屋苑啲單位開補習社(冇錯係違反地獒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）咁我想追一個miss，不過由於甚少同一時間放工，而且上堂時老闆又會係側邊，所以一直冇機會打開話匣子<br />\n<br />\n直到今日，終於可以同一時間收工，咁我就打算入lift就約佢食飯/傾下計，結果lift有人，咁我就諗住出去先講啦，點知一出去，腦海中出現上一段感情如何失敗<br />\n<br />\n有冇巴打可以屌醒我，令我開盡turbo追佢？或者比啲意見我更有效地追miss?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n sorry for 1999，中文作文攞2<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0eee3a0c687231a6bf4943598f0cdf2b88238875","tid":24171,"uid":9668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T11:36:08.000Z","msg":"冇心就返屋企啦"},{"pid":"fb4537e5bef274ed017e39015c75ead60727a886","tid":24171,"uid":1823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T11:40:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>冇心就返屋企啦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n點樣打開話題諗左成個月，連各種應變方法都諗左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申單身左3年 99.9%放低左"},{"pid":"08f4fd9f3c8c4d2b47bceceb7d826cc407882b7e","tid":24171,"uid":1823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T13:35:54.000Z","msg":"毒撚冇人理<img src=\"/as